Sleep, Screen Time and Stress Analysis:
Using a synthetic data set “Sleep, Screen Time and Stress Analysis” predict stress levels using machine learning models, analyze the impact of screen time on sleep quality.
The dataset includes the following types of information:
•	Demographic information (age, gender, occupation)
•	Daily smartphone usage patterns
•	Sleep duration and sleep quality indicators
•	Lifestyle factors such as caffeine intake and physical activity
•	Stress and mental fatigue indicators


